salesbox.Start360View: Get a 360° view of relations and communication
salesbox.Start360ViewDescription:
Track all your and your colleagues communications (dials, calls, emails , iMessages and faceTime).

 Keep all your tasks, appointments, leads, opportunities, progress, documents, photos & notes in one 360 view place.

Never again have anything slip through the cracks.
salesbox.StartCollaborate: Collaborate and be up to date
salesbox.StartCollaborateDescription:
Get updates in real-time and keep your colleagues up to date with your activities and progress. 

Work in joint processes and share accounts, contacts, opportunities, leads and tasks. 

Distribute to individuals or ticket lists and get notified on any updates wherever you are.
salesbox.StartGetEmpoweredDescription:
Get automatic tasks and action plans to see the effort needed to reach your targets.

Salesbox adapts to your individual behavior and performance and guides you to reach your targets.
salesbox.StartMakeRealuse: Make real use of your mobile devices
salesbox.StartMakeRealuseDescription:
Salesbox works silently, in the background, to automatically collect information for you. Salesbox is fully integrated with your iOS device to utilize your dial function, calendar, camera, contacts and maps function, so you never have to enter call statistics etc. manually.

Salesbox makes it easy to keep your colleagues and yourself up to date. Salesbox takes literarily seconds to update.
salesbox.StartWellCome: Welcome to your new personal business assistant
salesbox.StartZeroGAPDescription:
Create how many of your own business processes as you want. Choose which one to apply for each individual opportunity and eliminate the CRM process GAP to reality. 

Salesbox keeps track of your progress in real-time and keeps your forecasts and reports up to date.

salesbox.billingDescription:
If you recruit a user outside your own company you get to keep 20 % of the subscription fee paid by the recruited users. Salesbox will transfer the commission to your paypal account.

Any taxes and fees that may arise connected to the payment of the commission to you are bared by you. The commission is paid in USD.

It is not possible to recruit the same user for two different Salesbox users. Therefore a sent invitation will only be valid for 1 month. After that period is over it is possible for another Salesbox user to try and recruit the same user again.

salesbox.introPage.slide2.readmore:
Salesbox helps you focus on the right activities.

Salesbox guides you on what to do and prioritize.

Salesbox also proactively helps you to understand your target gap, so you never again need to worry about what it takes to reach your target.
salesbox.introPage.slide2.title: The No. 1 mobile CRM that guides the team to the sales target
salesbox.introPage.slide3.readmore: Salesbox is a truly mobile solution, built for the modern mobile business person who wants to stay informed and get active support 24/7. With Salesbox you have access to 100% of the functionality of your device, regardless of which mobile device you choose.
salesbox.introPage.slide3.title: Make more use of your iPhone/iPad/iPad Pro
salesbox.introPage.slide4.readmore:
Salesbox removes sandbagging and pipe dreams from your forecasts.

Salesbox lets the sales team focus on the activities that lead to closure and keep you informed when colleagues makes progress.

Salesbox automatically generates progress for each opportunity, based on which activities have been completed. This generates a uniform, trustworthy and real-time sales forecasting.
